{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/cfs-101-sch/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"zunione.blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ccd2e896-43f8-5fce-9e39-6787b2a4856d","excerpt":"🚀 들어가며 CFS-101 트레이닝의 마지막 파트에서는 기존 시스템을 재구성(reconfigure)하는 연습을 한다. 그 중 하나가 SCH(Scheduler) 애플리케이션의 동작 주파수를 기본 100Hz에서 40Hz로 변경하는 것이다. 이 글에서는 어떤 파일을 수정해야 하는지, 그리고 수정 시 주의할 점을 정리한다. 수정 대상 파일 변경이 필요한 파일은 …","html":"<h2 id=\"-들어가며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\" 들어가며 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>🚀 들어가며</h2>\n<p>CFS-101 트레이닝의 마지막 파트에서는 기존 시스템을 재구성(reconfigure)하는 연습을 한다. 그 중 하나가 SCH(Scheduler) 애플리케이션의 동작 주파수를 기본 100Hz에서 40Hz로 변경하는 것이다. 이 글에서는 어떤 파일을 수정해야 하는지, 그리고 수정 시 주의할 점을 정리한다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"수정-대상-파일\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95-%EB%8C%80%EC%83%81-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"수정 대상 파일 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>수정 대상 파일</h2>\n<p>변경이 필요한 파일은 <strong>2개</strong>다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-sch_platform_cfgh--슬롯-수-변경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-sch_platform_cfgh--%EC%8A%AC%EB%A1%AF-%EC%88%98-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"1 sch_platform_cfgh  슬롯 수 변경 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>1. <code class=\"language-text\">sch_platform_cfg.h</code> — 슬롯 수 변경</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">SCH_TOTAL_SLOTS</code> 값을 100에서 40으로 변경한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 변경 전 */</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">SCH_TOTAL_SLOTS</span>         <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">100</span>    </span><span class=\"token comment\">/* SCH wake-up rate (Hz) */</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* 변경 후 */</span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">SCH_TOTAL_SLOTS</span>         <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token number\">40</span>     </span><span class=\"token comment\">/* SCH wake-up rate (Hz) */</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이 값이 바뀌면 <code class=\"language-text\">SCH_TABLE_ENTRIES</code>도 자동으로 재계산된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">define</span> <span class=\"token macro-name\">SCH_TABLE_ENTRIES</span>       <span class=\"token expression\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>SCH_TOTAL_SLOTS <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> SCH_ENTRIES_PER_SLOT<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-sch_def_schtblc--스케줄-테이블-재배치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-sch_def_schtblc--%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84-%ED%85%8C%EC%9D%B4%EB%B8%94-%EC%9E%AC%EB%B0%B0%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"2 sch_def_schtblc  스케줄 테이블 재배치 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>2. <code class=\"language-text\">sch_def_schtbl.c</code> — 스케줄 테이블 재배치</h3>\n<p>스케줄 테이블은 <code class=\"language-text\">SCH_TABLE_ENTRIES</code> 크기의 배열이므로, 슬롯 #0~#39만 남기고 #40~#99를 삭제해야 한다. 문제는 <strong>슬롯 #40 이후에 활성 엔트리가 존재</strong>한다는 점이다.</p>\n<p>기존 테이블에서 #40 이후에 있던 활성 엔트리 3개를 #0~#39 범위의 빈 슬롯으로 이동시켜야 한다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>원래 슬롯</th>\n<th>내용</th>\n<th>이동할 슬롯</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>#43</td>\n<td>ES HK Request</td>\n<td>→ #4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>#49</td>\n<td>SCH HK Request</td>\n<td>→ #6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>#56</td>\n<td>CI HK Request + TO HK Request</td>\n<td>→ #8</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"슬롯-4--기존-43의-ES-HK\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%AC%EB%A1%AF-4--%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-43%EC%9D%98-ES-HK\" aria-label=\"슬롯 4  기존 43의 ES HK permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>슬롯 #4 (← 기존 #43의 ES HK)</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\">  <span class=\"token comment\">/* slot #4 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_ENABLED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_ACTIVITY_SEND_MSG<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  CFE_ES_SEND_HK_MIDX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> SCH_GROUP_CFE_HK <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">/* ES HK Request */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"슬롯-6--기존-49의-SCH-HK\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%AC%EB%A1%AF-6--%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-49%EC%9D%98-SCH-HK\" aria-label=\"슬롯 6  기존 49의 SCH HK permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.