span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"슬롯-8--기존-56의-CITO-HK\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%AC%EB%A1%AF-8--%EA%B8%B0%EC%A1%B4-56%EC%9D%98-CITO-HK\" aria-label=\"슬롯 8  기존 56의 CITO HK permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>슬롯 #8 (← 기존 #56의 CI/TO HK)</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\">  <span class=\"token comment\">/* slot #8 */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_ENABLED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_ACTIVITY_SEND_MSG<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> CI_SEND_HK_MIDX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> SCH_GROUP_NONE <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">/* CI HK Request */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_ENABLED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_ACTIVITY_SEND_MSG<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> TO_SEND_HK_MIDX<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> SCH_GROUP_NONE <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">/* TO HK Request */</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>  SCH_UNUSED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>      <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  SCH_GROUP_NONE<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이동할 슬롯은 기존에 비어있던 곳 중 아무 곳이나 골라도 된다. 다만 한 슬롯에 activity를 너무 몰아넣으면 해당 minor frame 안에 처리가 끝나지 않을 수 있으므로 적당히 분산시키는 것이 좋다.</p>\n<p>이동 후 슬롯 #40~#99를 전부 삭제하고, 배열의 마지막 원소(슬롯 #39의 마지막 엔트리)에서 trailing comma를 제거하면 된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"변경하지-않는-파일\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EB%8A%94-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"변경하지 않는 파일 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>변경하지 않는 파일</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">sch_def_msgtbl.c</code> (Message Definition Table)는 수정할 필요가 없다. 이 테이블의 크기는 <code class=\"language-text\">SCH_MAX_MESSAGES</code>(128)로 결정되며 슬롯 수와는 무관하다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"Frequency--Remainder는-괜찮을까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#Frequency--Remainder%EB%8A%94-%EA%B4%9C%EC%B0%AE%EC%9D%84%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"Frequency  Remainder는 괜찮을까 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>Frequency / Remainder는 괜찮을까?</h2>\n<p>스케줄 테이블의 각 엔트리에는 <code class=\"language-text\">Frequency</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">Remainder</code> 필드가 있다. 예를 들어 <code class=\"language-text\">Frequency=4, Remainder=3</code>은 \"4번째 major frame마다 실행\"을 의미한다.</p>\n<p>Major frame 1개는 전체 슬롯을 한 바퀴 도는 주기다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>100Hz, 100슬롯</strong> → major frame = 100 ÷ 100 = <strong>1초</strong></li>\n<li><strong>40Hz, 40슬롯</strong> → major frame = 40 ÷ 40 = <strong>1초</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>슬롯 수와 Hz를 함께 변경했으므로 major frame 주기는 동일하게 1초로 유지된다. 따라서 <code class=\"language-text\">Frequency=4</code>인 HK request는 여전히 4초마다 실행되며, 기존과 동작이 달라지지 않는다.</p>\n<p>만약 슬롯 수만 줄이고 Hz를 그대로 뒀다면 (40슬롯에 100Hz) major frame이 0.4초가 되어 의도치 않게 주기가 빨라지는 문제가 발생할 수 있으니 주의해야 한다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"동작-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"동작 확인 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>동작 확인</h2>\n<p>빌드 후 <code class=\"language-text\">core-cpu1</code>을 실행하면 다음과 같이 정상 동작을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">EVS Port1 42/1/SCH 1: SCH Initialized. Version 2.2.1.0\n...\nEVS Port1 42/1/TEMP_MON 1: TEMP_MON - HkTlm - Temp=1, Dir=1, Range=2\nEVS Port1 42/1/TEMP_MON 1: TEMP_MON - HkTlm - Temp=2, Dir=1, Range=2\nEVS Port1 42/1/TEMP_MON 1: TEMP_MON - HkTlm - Temp=3, Dir=1, Range=2</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>모든 앱(CI, TO, TEMP_IO, TEMP_MON, SCH)이 정상 로딩됨</li>\n<li>cFE가 OPERATIONAL state에 진입</li>\n<li>TEMP_MON HK 텔레메트리가 주기적으로 출력됨</li>\n</ul>\n<p>GroundSystem의 Telemetry System에서 SCH HK 페이지의 <code class=\"language-text\">SlotsProcessedCount</code>가 초당 40씩 증가하고 있다면, 정확히 40Hz로 동작하고 있는 것이다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"정리 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>정리</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>파일</th>\n<th>수정 내용</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">sch_platform_cfg.h</code></td>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">SCH_TOTAL_SLOTS</code>를 100 → 40으로 변경</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">sch_def_schtbl.c</code></td>\n<td>슬롯 #40 이후의 활성 엔트리를 #0~#39로 재배치 후, #40~#99 삭제</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">sch_def_msgtbl.c</code></td>\n<td>변경 불필요</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"-마치며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EB%A7%88%EC%B9%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\" 마치며 permalink\" class=\"heading-anchor before\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6.188 8.719c.439-.439.926-.801 1.444-1.087 2.887-1.591 6.589-.745 8.445 2.069l-2.246 2.245c-.644-1.469-2.243-2.305-3.834-1.949-.599.134-1.168.433-1.633.898l-4.304 4.306c-1.307 1.307-1.307 3.433 0 4.74 1.307 1.307 3.433 1.307 4.74 0l1.327-1.327c1.207.479 2.501.67 3.779.575l-2.929 2.929c-2.511 2.511-6.582 2.511-9.093 0s-2.511-6.582 0-9.093l4.304-4.306zm6.836-6.836l-2.929 2.929c1.277-.096 2.572.096 3.779.574l1.326-1.326c1.307-1.307 3.433-1.307 4.74 0 1.307 1.307 1.307 3.433 0 4.74l-4.305 4.305c-1.311 1.311-3.44 1.3-4.74 0-.303-.303-.564-.68-.727-1.051l-2.246 2.245c.236.358.481.667.796.982.812.812 1.846 1.417 3.036 1.704 1.542.371 3.194.166 4.613-.617.518-.286 1.005-.648 1.444-1.087l4.304-4.305c2.512-2.511 2.512-6.582.001-9.093-2.511-2.51-6.581-2.51-9.092 0z\"/></svg></a>✨ 마치며</h2>","frontmatter":{"title":"[cFS] CFS-101(7): SCH 추가과제","date":"April 09, 2026","update":"April 09, 2026","tags":["nasa-cfs","fsw"],"series":"NASA cFS로 우주 소프트웨어 개발자 되기"},"fields":{"slug":"/cfs-101-sch/","readingTime":{"minutes":4}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"850e4986-daa9-55af-977f-f87267685e24","fields":{"slug":"/cfs-basic-structure/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[cFS] NASA cFS 소프트웨어의 기본 구조"}}},{"node":{"id":"40656005-9508-5b4a-94fc-5bf644d3ed20","fields":{"slug":"/cfs-101-core/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[cFS] CFS-101(1): cFE Core Apps 빌드 및 실행"}}},{"node":{"id":"dadab148-d181-5133-a7be-3e29feeb0ca1","fields":{"slug":"/cfs-101-groundsystem/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[cFS] CFS-101(2): GroundSystem으로 위성체와 지상국 간 통신 실습하기"}}},{"node":{"id":"bbedf076-aac7-5743-b32a-67026ea78c9d","fields":{"slug":"/cfs-101-new-app/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[cFS] CFS-101(3): 새로운 앱을 추가해 나만의 FSW 만들기"}}},{"node"